title: 210. Q&AF: Fat Andy, Boss Andy & Cheap Andy
itunes:title: 210. Q&AF: Fat Andy, Boss Andy & Cheap Andy
description: In today's episode, Andy answers your questions on what triggered him to make a weight loss & lifestyle change, when's the right time to transition into owning multiple companies, and if there's anything he would NOT spend his money on.
